body:
It’s easy to stay ahead of the fashion pack with Myer’s huge range of young and contemporary footwear brands. They’re all about hot-right-now footwear styles at prices to suit everyone’s budget.


Tap into our collection of most wanted young and contemporary brands in this Learning Moment.
title: AHEAD_OF_THE_PACK

body:
"Our youth customer loves social media and follows all the latest trends. Our range gives them all the looks they want, always at a competitive price."


Renee Hallam

Category Buyer, Young and Contemporary Footwear
title: Text Title

body:
Miss Shop caters for shoe fanatics, with all the latest fashion footwear styles in a wide range of colours. Whether you’re on the hunt for heels, flats, sandals, sneakers or boots, make Miss Shop your first stop.


Miss Shop is exclusive to Myer and uses non-leather upper, lining and sole.


The range falls within the $59.95 - $99.95 price range.
title: Text Title

body:
Established in 1946 as a manufacturer of biker boots for men, Windsor Smith is now Australia’s number one mens and womens fashion footwear brand. The brand name reflects how the shoes are suitable for everybody from the Smiths to the Windsors.


Windsor Smith uses leather uppers, and non-leather lining and sole.


Prices from $99.95 to $199.95 for boots.

body:
Piper footwear is continuously redefining urban style with casual cool styling at great value prices.


Piper footwear is exclusive to Myer and features leather uppers and non-leather lining and soles.


Prices from $99.95 up to $199.95 for boots.
title: Text Title

body:
Wayne Cooper shoes offer effortless glamour for women who dare to take risks.


Wayne Cooper uses leather uppers, non-leather lining and soles, and is exclusive to Myer.


Prices from $149.95 to $199.95 for boots.
title: Text Title

body: Get ready for it. Here are more of our hottest young and contemporary footwear brands.

_items.body:
Lipstik shoes set the pace in fun, fresh and fashionable footwear at an amazing price.


Prices from $79.95 and up to $129.95 for boots.

Starting out in Queens, New York, in the 1990s, the Steve Madden brand has become synonymous with rock and roll inspired footwear for on-trend women and men around the world.


Prices from $109.95 to $239.95

Born and raised in Melbourne, Siren makes no apologies for its bold approach to fashion. For the past decade Siren has been leading the market with inspirational footwear.


Prices from $139.95, and up to $299.95 for long boots.
